# MEME Suite custom alphabet: DMP project DNA palette
# Matches the DMP gene family visualization colors.
# Gray adenine, golden amber cytosine, warm peach guanine, dark orange thymine.
# Usage:  meme --alph dmp_dna.alph <sequences> ...
ALPHABET "DNA DMP" DNA-LIKE
A "Adenine" B3B3B3 ~ T "Thymine" E69F00
C "Cytosine" D9A621 ~ G "Guanine" FFB366
# Ambiguous symbols
U = T
R = AG
Y = CT
K = GT
M = AC
S = CG
W = AT
B = CGT
D = GAT
H = ACT
V = ACG
N = ACGT
X = ACGT
